Package soffico.customerapi.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64Helper
    Helper class with methods to deal with bas64 data.
    BinaryHelper
    Helper class with methods to deal with byte arrays.
    DateConverter
    This class encapsulates all functions for date conversions
    DeprecationHandler
    This class is used to send a deprecation signal whenever customer API functions are used that will be refactored in the future.
    JsonHelper
    Helper class with methods to deal with strings containing JSON arrays.
    TypeHelper
    Helper class providing methods to create and convert values to be assigned to Parameters in a process model.
    UniqueCounter
    This class encapsulates all functions for generating unique identifiers within orchestra
